Well, Randy, thanks for
joining us on the show today.

00:39:36.360 --> 00:39:37.970 align:middle line:84%
It's always a pleasure
to have you on.

00:39:37.970 --> 00:39:38.700 align:middle line:90%
>>CRAMER: Thank you.

